          "reviewBody": "Today I went to take an competitive exam at this school (17.12.2023). After the exam, when I wanted to go to the bathroom, a guard spoke to me very badly.  I want to know if your school children are taught to urinate under trees?  That's what I was told when I wanted to go to the bathroom today.",
